Install minikube

https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/



to apply deployment in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_deployment.yaml

to apply services in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_services.yaml

to apply secrets in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_secrets.yaml

-----------------------------------------

to show all

kubectl get all

to show Pods, Deployment, Services and Secrets

kubectl get deployment 

kubectl get services

kubectl get secrets

kubectl get pods

--------CONFIGURATION-----------

to check status 

kubectl get $name --watch


to check problem 

example
kubectl describe pod $pod_name

to check specific

kubectl get all | grep $name


to check logs


kubectl logs $name



